1. Overview of the Framework for DE

This implementation develops an Intrusion Detection System (IDS) using:

Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) deep learning
Differential Evolution (DE) for hyperparameter optimization
Differential Privacy Stochastic Gradient Descent (DP-SGD)
TensorFlow Privacy for privacy-preserving learning

The framework performs two major experiments:

Non-private optimized LSTM model
Differentially private optimized LSTM model

The objective is to evaluate the privacy–utility trade-off between predictive performance and privacy guarantees.

