6. Differential Privacy Libraries
import tensorflow_privacy
from tensorflow_privacy.privacy.analysis import compute_dp_sgd_privacy
Explanation

TensorFlow Privacy provides DP-SGD implementation.

DP-SGD modifies standard SGD using:

Gradient clipping
Noise injection

The DP guarantee is expressed as:

(ε,δ)-DP

Where:

ε controls privacy leakage
δ is failure probability

Smaller ε indicates stronger privacy.

